---
title: Pork and Zucchini Bolognese with Spinach and Parmesan
description: We've put a summer-inspired twist on this Italian classic by adding zucchini and spinach. Mixed with juicy pork and a sprinkling of Parmesan, all these ingredients blend to create an incredible depth of flavour.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/pork-and-zucchini-bolognese-b22dac9f.jpg
